signatures.text: fun <K, V> mapOf(vararg pairs: Pair<K, V>): Map<K, V>
signatures.desc: Returns a new read-only map with the specified contents, given as a list of pairs where the first value is the key and the second is the value.

signatures.text: fun <K, V> mapOf(pair: Pair<K, V>): Map<K, V>
signatures.desc: Returns an immutable map, mapping only the specified key to the specified value.
